Interface IndividualExpression

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface IndividualExpression
extends Individual<it.emarolab.amor.owlInterface.OWLReferences,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLNamedIndividual>, DescriptorGroundInterface<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLNamedIndividual>
    This interface extends all the interfaces in Individual. It allows to Axiom.Descriptor.readExpressionAxioms() and Axiom.Descriptor.writeExpressionAxioms() specifically for OWL Individuals. It contains several expressions that can be combined in any arbitrary way as they rely on the same ground (IndividualGroundInstance).
